highlights.text: “Night Changes” by One Direction has been on Top Songs Malaysia the longest, at 1640 days straight.
My Chemical Romance has the most spots on Top Songs Malaysia. “I Don't Love You” is the highest at #13.
“Sampai Menutup Mata” by Acha Septriasa is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Malaysia, up 66 spots at #133.
